{
  "stem": "2226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He brought the chain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He brought it right away [LAUGHS] all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a million dollar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I were-- I almost said, if that's the case, I can make the chains in one day, because tomorrow it might be throw me out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I told the civilian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That has to take me longer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because of the-- the locks, I can make it like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have to make everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he went to that oberkapo and told the oberkapo, listen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That man knows what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that-- that where I was staying already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he brought every day a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was supposed to make it in two weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he comes one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I had a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You gonna make me the chain?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Is it gonna be in summer?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Listen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said to me, I know it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want the bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's not the point, the bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sure, though, the bread is very important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And over there, when I was over there, I could have a hot water too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I made myself a-- from of piece of pipe-- a-- a kettle-- you know, well done on the bottom-- the-- underneath the bottom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, how you cook?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can't see the steam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's no good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where you gonna cook?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I took a piece of steel, heavy steel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's assume I had-- as a big piece like that plate-- the left plate-- very heavy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I put that over there with the blacksmith, you know, where to cook.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we heat that up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's like you got to have plate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you don't have to have.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Water, yeah, but they know as soon as I said--",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
